  "title": "Senior Consultant (Government) / Assistant Manager (Infrastructure)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Consultant (Government) / Assistant Manager (Infrastructure)</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Key contact to the customers in the public safety sector.</strong></li><li><strong>Involed in the developing of the next breakthrough for the security of Singapore.</strong></li><li>Responsible for developing, testing and deploying system/network infrastructure.</li><li>Involved in Project Planning, Scheduling and Budget Management.</li><li>Responsible for IT Projects maintenance, scoping, resource allocation, scheduling, budgeting, and risk management.</li><li>Involved in Contractual obligations and service level agreements (SLAs).</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Strong experience in managing Government accounts.</strong></li><li><strong>Meet potential clients by growing, maintaining, and leveraging your network</strong></li><li><strong>Strong in managing client's needs, concerns, and objectives.</strong></li><li><strong>Good in providing solutions, advisory, consultation and delivery.</strong></li><li><strong>Involved in </strong>IT Infrastructure maintenance or IT System Integration.</li><li>Experience in leading a team.</li><li><strong>Good in Network/ System Infrastructure Deployment and Testing.</strong></li><li><strong>Knowledge of Public Security.</strong></li><li>Good in Stakeholders, Client Management and Business Users Management.</li><li>Knowledge of Network, Cyber Security, IT Infrastructure, Switching, Routing, Firewall and IT Service Management.</li><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in IT Infrastructure and Lead experience.</li><li><strong>Possess Government (Defence) domain (preferred).</strong></li><li>Degree in Computer Science/ Business or Engineering.</li><li>Singaporeans only</li></ul><p></p><p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : jeline@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p><br /></p><p>Yong Jeline (Reg. No. R1101621)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
